# ==============================================================================
# MULTI-CHAIN CONFIGURATION SYSTEM
# ==============================================================================
# This project supports multiple blockchain networks.
#
# Available Chain-Specific Configurations:
# - .env.sepolia (ETH Sepolia) - Latest deployment with vesting & dependency features
# - .env.opsepolia (OP Sepolia) - Archived deployment
#
# To switch networks:
# 1. Copy the content from the desired .env.{chain} file
# 2. Paste it into the main .env file
# 3. Restart your development server
# ==============================================================================

# Blockchain Configuration
